title: Stocks to Watch: Preparing Your Portfolio for Higher Interest Rates
description: Barron's senior managing editor Lauren R. Rublin and deputy editor Ben Levisohn discuss what the Federal Reserve's plan to raise interest rates means for financial markets, industry sectors, and individual stocks.
